I'm actually quite pleased.

582
00:38:18,190 --> 00:38:19,500
Why add more distress to myself

583
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:20,690
by being hungry?

584
00:38:23,070 --> 00:38:24,540
What did I say before?

585
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:26,190
The wedding date is still early.

586
00:38:26,190 --> 00:38:27,500
Many changes can happen.

587
00:38:28,670 --> 00:38:30,250
You just didn't believe it.

588
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:37,810
This place is better.

589
00:38:41,760 --> 00:38:44,380
It's cold and damp here all year round.

590
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:47,460
I'm afraid that Miantang's hand injury

591
00:38:47,720 --> 00:38:48,610
will be hard to endure.

592
00:38:48,990 --> 00:38:50,100
Don't worry.

593
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:51,610
I've checked for you.

594
00:38:52,590 --> 00:38:54,290
She's had the medicine patch on for so long

595
00:38:54,510 --> 00:38:55,980
that her hand injury has healed a lot.

596
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:58,210
Will it fully recover?

597
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:01,030
It's a torn tendon,

598
00:39:01,030 --> 00:39:02,250
not just a scrape.

599
00:39:02,550 --> 00:39:04,290
It's not that easy to fully recover.

600
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:07,250
Unless

601
00:39:07,510 --> 00:39:08,760
we can find the rare

602
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:10,100
eagle flower for medicine.

603
00:39:12,590 --> 00:39:13,710
Then go find it.

604
00:39:13,710 --> 00:39:15,060
Tell me how much money you need.

605
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,580
Fine, I'll help you find it.

606
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:22,920
For now, there's another method that can be

607
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:24,170
used as a substitute.

608
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:26,160
What method?

609
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:27,330
I've found

610
00:39:27,470 --> 00:39:29,060
a hot spring nearby.

611
00:39:29,880 --> 00:39:31,590
Using it for the tendon

612
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:32,670
and blood

613
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:33,650
is the best remedy.

614
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:44,210
Here we are.

615
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:51,030
I didn't expect there to be

616
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:52,460
a good hot spring in the northwest.

617
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:53,960
The Lord instructed us

618
00:39:53,960 --> 00:39:54,810
to survey nearby.

619
00:39:55,150 --> 00:39:56,190
When we found this spring,

620
00:39:56,190 --> 00:39:57,330
he rewarded us with it,

621
00:39:57,760 --> 00:40:00,020
allowing soldiers with merits to use it.

622
00:40:00,920 --> 00:40:01,760
Dear,

623
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:03,420
you can go to the small tent

624
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:04,540
and change your clothes.

625
00:40:06,630 --> 00:40:07,690
This place is wonderful.

626
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:09,510
The Lord does care for his subordinates.

627
00:40:09,510 --> 00:40:10,900
He even prepared a small tent.

628
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:12,980
- I'll go change then.
- Go ahead.

629
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:20,200
Moru,

630
00:40:20,990 --> 00:40:21,900
prepare the blanket

631
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:23,330
and wait at the bottom.

632
00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:25,080
Yes.

633
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:01,860
Dear, don't just stand there.

634
00:41:02,240 --> 00:41:03,980
It's windy. Take care not to catch a cold.

635
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:05,330
Hurry and get in.

636
00:41:23,030 --> 00:41:24,860
The hot spring water is so warm.

637
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:27,170
It will help with the tendon and blood.

638
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:28,630
Honey, come down quickly.

639
00:41:28,630 --> 00:41:29,470
Alright.

640
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:35,610
What's the matter?

641
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:39,960
This hot spring

642
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:42,130
was set up by the Lord for the soldiers.

643
00:41:43,070 --> 00:41:45,290
I was only able to get this opportunity for you

644
00:41:45,630 --> 00:41:47,730
because the general showed mercy.

645
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:50,900
The other military families did not come.

646
00:41:51,190 --> 00:41:52,980
If I were to join you in the bath,

647
00:41:53,470 --> 00:41:54,650
the comrades

648
00:41:54,990 --> 00:41:55,830
would laugh at me.

649
00:41:57,920 --> 00:41:59,420
You may get cold leaving the water.

650
00:41:59,550 --> 00:42:00,900
I've prepared a hot drink for you.

651
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:04,580
I thought of that too,

652
00:42:04,840 --> 00:42:06,330
so I also brought some medicinal wine.

653
00:42:06,440 --> 00:42:07,280
Don't come up.

654
00:42:08,070 --> 00:42:09,380
You might catch a cold like this.

655
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:10,650
Where is it? I'll get it.

656
00:42:10,990 --> 00:42:11,860
It's in the basket.

657
00:42:17,030 --> 00:42:19,060
The medicinal wine is effective
against the cold.

658
00:42:20,470 --> 00:42:21,440
I didn't know

659
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:22,650
you could make medicinal wine.

660
00:42:26,110 --> 00:42:27,150
Can it be drunk?

661
00:42:27,150 --> 00:42:28,250
Of course.

662
00:42:28,470 --> 00:42:29,920
I got this nourishing recipe

663
00:42:29,920 --> 00:42:31,330
from Physician Zhao.

664
00:42:31,510 --> 00:42:32,760
I searched the shop to gather

665
00:42:32,760 --> 00:42:33,630
all the ingredients.

666
00:42:33,630 --> 00:42:35,290
It's been soaking for a whole night.

667
00:42:36,360 --> 00:42:37,400
It's perfect for you

668
00:42:37,400 --> 00:42:38,580
since you have an injury.

669
00:42:44,150 --> 00:42:44,990
It's bitter.

670
00:42:45,550 --> 00:42:46,390
Really?

671
00:42:46,670 --> 00:42:48,610
Then next time I'll add some rock candy.

672
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:49,990
It's alright.

673
00:42:50,550 --> 00:42:51,420
I can drink

674
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:52,770
anything you make.

675
00:43:28,221 --> 00:43:34,451
♪The boat drifts,
bringing back the sunset♪

676
00:43:35,451 --> 00:43:41,571
♪When we reunite, we still joke
about the cause and effect♪

677
00:43:42,561 --> 00:43:48,811
♪Who passed by, the crabapple
falls with a turn♪

678
00:43:49,941 --> 00:43:53,181
♪Loving rightly but choosing wrong♪

679
00:43:53,521 --> 00:43:58,101
♪With joys, sorrows, partings and reunions♪

680
00:43:58,701 --> 00:44:05,361
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

681
00:44:06,111 --> 00:44:09,481
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

682
00:44:09,771 --> 00:44:13,101
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

683
00:44:13,281 --> 00:44:20,051
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

684
00:44:20,431 --> 00:44:27,201
♪Long hidden in the eyes,
flickering in and out♪

685
00:44:27,701 --> 00:44:34,111
♪Let go of the flowers blooming
in the yard last night♪

686
00:44:34,951 --> 00:44:41,361
♪Let go of the waves in the stream
in half a lifetime♪

687
00:44:41,941 --> 00:44:48,561
♪Let those dust and chaos go on endlessly♪

688
00:44:49,361 --> 00:44:52,781
♪In this lifetime, my wish is to the vast sky♪

689
00:44:52,781 --> 00:44:57,881
♪There are many more♪

690
00:44:58,261 --> 00:45:04,981
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

691
00:45:05,551 --> 00:45:09,181
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

692
00:45:09,181 --> 00:45:12,581
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

693
00:45:12,581 --> 00:45:19,491
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

694
00:45:19,781 --> 00:45:26,631
♪Time flows as we dream through four seasons♪

695
00:45:27,001 --> 00:45:30,581
♪I wish to journey with you forever♪

696
00:45:30,581 --> 00:45:33,691
♪Year after year♪

697
00:45:35,421 --> 00:45:39,721
♪For many years to come♪
